fields.name: sql
fields.value:
SELECT 
  household_key,
  CASE WHEN AGE_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', AGE_DESC, '\'') ELSE AGE_DESC END AS age_desc,
  CASE WHEN MARITAL_STATUS_CODE LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', MARITAL_STATUS_CODE, '\'') ELSE MARITAL_STATUS_CODE END AS marital_status_code,
  CASE WHEN INCOME_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', INCOME_DESC, '\'') ELSE INCOME_DESC END AS income_desc,
  CASE WHEN HOMEOWNER_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', HOMEOWNER_DESC, '\'') ELSE HOMEOWNER_DESC END AS homeowner_desc,
  CASE WHEN HH_COMP_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', HH_COMP_DESC, '\'') ELSE HH_COMP_DESC END AS hh_comp_desc,
  CASE WHEN HOUSEHOLD_SIZE_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', HOUSEHOLD_SIZE_DESC, '\'') ELSE HOUSEHOLD_SIZE_DESC END AS household_size_desc,
  CASE WHEN KID_CATEGORY_DESC LIKE '%-%' THEN CONCAT('\'', KID_CATEGORY_DESC, '\'') ELSE KID_CATEGORY_DESC END AS kid_category_desc,

  Camp_1 AS camp_1,
  Camp_2 AS camp_2,
  Camp_3 AS camp_3,
  Camp_4 AS camp_4,
  Camp_5 AS camp_5,
  Camp_6 AS camp_6,
  Camp_7 AS camp_7,
  Camp_8 AS camp_8,
  Camp_9 AS camp_9,
  Camp_10 AS camp_10,
  Camp_11 AS camp_11,
  Camp_12 AS camp_12,
  Camp_13 AS camp_13,
  Camp_14 AS camp_14,
  Camp_15 AS camp_15,
  Camp_16 AS camp_16,
  Camp_17 AS camp_17,
  Camp_18 AS camp_18,
  Camp_19 AS camp_19,
  Camp_20 AS camp_20,
  Camp_21 AS camp_21,
  Camp_22 AS camp_22,
  Camp_23 AS camp_23,
  Camp_24 AS camp_24,
  Camp_25 AS camp_25,
  Camp_26 AS camp_26,
  Camp_27 AS camp_27,
  Camp_28 AS camp_28,
  Camp_29 AS camp_29,
  Camp_30 AS camp_30,

  no_of_received_campaigns AS no_of_received_campaigns,

  Store_450 AS store_450,
  Store_318 AS store_318,
  Store_289 AS store_289,
  Store_404 AS store_404,
  Store_31582 AS store_31582,
  Store_372 AS store_372,
  Store_335 AS store_335,
  Store_298 AS store_298,
  Store_381 AS store_381,
  Store_412 AS store_412,
  Store_380 AS store_380,
  Store_424 AS store_424,
  Store_343 AS store_343,
  Store_421 AS store_421,
  Store_321 AS store_321,
  Store_433 AS store_433,
  Store_319 AS store_319,
  Store_320 AS store_320,
  Store_375 AS store_375,
  Store_292 AS store_292,

  no_of_redeems AS no_of_redeems,
  most_freq_camp_type AS most_freq_camp_type,
  TotalPurchaseUSD AS total_purchase_usd,
  isChurned AS is_churned,
  Total_sales AS total_sales,
  total_visits AS total_visits,
  median_basket AS median_basket,
  avg_price AS avg_price,
  prediction AS prediction

FROM fire_temp_table;
